SinnLeffers Retail Chain Returns to Profit, Sueddeutsche Says

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-08-08T07:40:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-08/sinnleffers-retail-chain-returns-to-profit-sueddeutsche-says.html
SinnLeffers GmbH posted a profit in
the fiscal year that ended July 31, the sole fashion chain
formerly belonging to  Arcandor AG (ARO)  to manage a turnaround,
Sueddeutsche Zeitung reported.  Earnings were “clearly in the black” and gross sales
climbed 6 percent to “significantly” more than 300 million
euros ($431 million), the German newspaper said, citing Co-Chief
Executive Officers Karsten Oberheide and Abram Nette.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sheenagh Matthews in Frankfurt at 
 smatthews6@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net  